riving-tomorrow-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-finals"><em>Finals</em></a>宣布了即将推出的免费射击游戏的另一个测试版，玩家将能够获得游戏内的额外奖励并保留它们以供发布。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-fps-games-2979649">最佳 FPS 游戏：2023 年您能玩到的最佳射击游戏是什么？</a></strong></li></ul><p>该活动将于 10 月 26 日至 11 月 5 日举行，面向<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>玩家开放，并且是允许跨平台游戏的公开测试版。</p><p>内测中的两张地图将回归，摩纳哥和首尔，并将推出名为 Skyway Stadium 的新地图。 </p><figure id="attachment_3521321" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521321" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3521321" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521321" class="wp-caption-text"> “总决赛”来源：Embark Studios</figcaption></figure><p>在进入四种游戏模式之一之前，玩家可以在练习场中掌握<em>总决赛的</em>机制和动作。</p><p>兑现涉及三名玩家组成的团队，他们将竞相寻找钱箱，保护它们，然后将它们存入金库。在规定轮数结束时现金最多的球队将获胜。</p><p> Cashout 有 Ranked 和 UnRanked 版本，前者使用 48 名玩家，四轮，后者使用 24 名玩家，三轮。</p><p> Quick Cash 是一种“休闲友好”模式，具有更宽松的重生计时器、提取时间，并且一次只有一个金库。 </p><figure id="attachment_3521320" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521320" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3521320" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521320" class="wp-caption-text"> “总决赛”来源：Embark Studios</figcaption></figure><p>另外，新的 Bank-It 模式是一种“以战斗为中心”的体验，四支由三名玩家组成的队伍在回合结束时争夺金币，成为最富有的队伍。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/embark-studios">Embark Studios</a>还为<em>The Finals</em>公测版添加了战斗通行证，玩家可以在游戏完整发布时保留 16 种独家奖励。</p><p>今年早些时候， <em>《NME》</em>将<em>《总决赛》</em>第一个测试版描述为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-finals-closed-beta-is-letting-me-live-my-dream-of-being-a-rpg-toting-panda-3411002">一场无休止的枪声和爆炸的狗屎秀</a>”，它并没有完全兑现预告片中所承诺的破坏性。</p><p> “这款游戏将自己定位为一款不太认真的游戏：愚蠢的服装和播音员的低声叫喊使这款游戏与你可能会从一款由<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/dice">DICE</a>老兵，”杰克·塔克 (Jake Tucker) 说道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，演员本·斯塔尔 (Ben Starr)、道格·科克 (Doug Cockle)、亚历克斯·乔丹 (Alex Jordan) 和哈利·麦肯泰尔 (Harry McEntire) 以及游戏名人霍莉·贝内特 (Hollie Bennett) 和奥伊芙·威尔逊 (Aoife Wilson) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/natural-six-dungeons-and-dragons-ben-starr-hollie-bennett-3520470">正在制作新的<em>《龙与地下城》</em>系列</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-finals-beta-revealed-for-pc-ps5-and-xbox-series-xs-3521299">针对 PC、PS5 和 Xbox Series X|S 的“总决赛”测试版</a>后发布首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
